OL,3,CAnthony Gordon undergoes medical
OL,4,Cbefore #69m Barcelona transfer
OL,6,FEngland forward Anthony Gordon is
OL,7,Ftravelling to Spain as he closes in on
OL,8,Fa #69m move from Newcastle to
OL,9,FBarcelona.
OL,11,FGordon is heading to Catalonia to
OL,12,Fundergo a medical after the two clubs
OL,13,Fagreed on a fee for the 25-year-old.
OL,15,FAccording to reports the Spanish
OL,16,Fchampions have agreed to pay the
OL,17,FMagpies in excess of 80m euros `
OL,18,Faround #69.3m ` to sign a player they
OL,19,Ffaced in the Champions League this
OL,20,Fseason.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
