OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1780225373
OL,3,CAnthony Gordon undergoes medical
OL,4,Cbefore #69m Barcelona transfer
OL,6,FGordon had also attracted attention
OL,7,Ffrom Bayern Munich and a host of other
OL,8,Fsuitors, and Newcastle will have been
OL,9,Fkeen to act quickly after the
OL,10,Ffrustration of last summer and
OL,11,FAlexander Isak's protracted move to
OL,12,FLiverpool.
OL,14,FThe deal will also see the Magpies
OL,15,Fboost their coffers with a significant
OL,16,Fprofit on the #45m they paid Everton
OL,17,Fin January 2023 at a time when they
OL,18,Fare looking to rebuild after a
OL,19,Fdisappointing campaign.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
