OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1780225373
OL,3,CAnthony Gordon undergoes medical
OL,4,Cbefore #69m Barcelona transfer
OL,6,FAs the rumour mill went into full
OL,7,Fswing with the end of the campaign
OL,8,Fapproaching, Newcastle boss Eddie Howe
OL,9,Fdecided to leave the player out of his
OL,10,Fteam on his return from injury, citing
OL,11,Fthe need to focus on the future.
OL,13,FIf the deal is completed, Gordon will
OL,14,Fbecome the sixth member of Thomas
OL,15,FTuchel's World Cup squad at an
OL,16,Foverseas club, joining Harry Kane,
OL,17,FJude Bellingham, Marcus Rashford, Ivan
OL,18,FToney and Jarell Quansah.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
